{
  "uid": "v12-0-sql-expr",
  "title": "Grafana 12.0 \u2014 SQL Expressions",
  "description": "Demonstrates SQL Expressions (MySQL dialect) running on top of two Prometheus queries. Requires the `sqlExpressions` feature toggle (enabled in .env). Query A fetches HTTP request rates by handler; query B fetches average durations; the SQL expression joins the two and sorts by busiest.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "v12.0",
    "sql-expressions",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-15m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_prom",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prom"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10000,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "tags": [
        "demo-guide"
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1.2rem;background:#1a2a3a;border-left:4px solid #5794f2;border-radius:6px;font-family:system-ui\"><div style=\"font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8aa9d0;margin-bottom:.3rem\">DEMO GUIDE</div><div style=\"font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Grafana 12.0 \u2014 SQL Expressions</div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem\"><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#5794f2;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83c\udfaf What you're looking at</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">v12.0 SQL Expressions let you JOIN results from different data sources with a SQL SELECT. Think 'SELECT \u2026 FROM A JOIN B' across Prom + Postgres in one panel.</div></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#73bf69;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83e\uddea Try this</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Edit the panel \u2014 the third query (refId: SQL) is plain SQL operating on the rows from refId A and B. Change the SQL to add a WHERE clause.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:.8rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:1px solid #2d3e54;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udcda <strong style=\"color:#fff\">Learn more</strong>: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/panels-visualizations/query-transform-data/expression-queries/#sql-expressions\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Grafana docs</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/whatsnew/whats-new-in-v12-0/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">v12 What's New</a></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### SQL Expressions\n\n**Enabled by:** `GF_FEATURE_TOGGLES_ENABLE=sqlExpressions` (already set in this lab).\n\nYou can join results from different data sources with a SQL SELECT. This dashboard joins two Prometheus queries on the `handler` label. Panel below is the joined result; the SQL is in the query tab \u2014 click *Edit* on the panel."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "HTTP handlers \u2014 rate vs avg latency (SQL joined)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 14,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "__expr__",
        "type": "__expr__"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "uid": "${ds_prom}",
            "type": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (handler) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "uid": "${ds_prom}",
            "type": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by (handler) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_sum[$__rate_interval])) / sum by (handler) (rate(grafana_http_request_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "SQL",
          "datasource": {
            "uid": "__expr__",
            "type": "__expr__"
          },
          "type": "sql",
          "expression": "SELECT A.handler AS handler, A.\"Value\" AS req_per_sec, B.\"Value\" AS avg_latency_sec FROM A LEFT JOIN B ON A.handler = B.handler ORDER BY req_per_sec DESC LIMIT 25"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "filterable": true
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "req_per_sec"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "reqps"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 3
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "color-background",
                  "mode": "gradient"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "thresholds",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "absolute",
                  "steps": [
                    {
                      "color": "green",
                      "value": null
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "orange",
                      "value": 1
                    },
                    {
                      "color": "red",
                      "value": 10
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "avg_latency_sec"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "s"
              },
              {
                "id": "decimals",
                "value": 4
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                "value": {
                  "type": "gauge",
                  "mode": "gradient"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "max",
                "value": 0.2
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm"
      },
      "description": "HTTP handlers \u2014 rate vs avg latency (SQL joined). Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/panels-visualizations/query-transform-data/expression-queries/#sql-expressions"
    }
  ]
}